TI  - Exploring social networks in a small tank cascade system in Northcentral Sri Lanka: First steps to establishing adaptive governance
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL DEVELOPMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Small tank cascades
KW  - Social networks
KW  - Water governance
KW  - Climate adaptation
