TI  - Climate-smart agricultural technology and gender-differentiated food, and water security: Evidence from smallholder sunflower ( Helianthus annuus L.) Farmers
T2  - AGRICULTURAL WATER MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Crop production
