TI  - Suitability of root, tuber, and banana crops in Central Africa can be favoured under future climates
T2  - AGRICULTURAL SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Root and tuber crops
KW  - Crop suitability
KW  - EcoCrop
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Central Africa
KW  - Smallholder farming
KW  - ADAPTATION
KW  - AGRICULTURE
KW  - TEMPERATURES
KW  - IMPACTS
