TI  - Coupling climate risks, eco-systems, and anthropogenic decisions using South American and Sub-Saharan farming activities
T2  - METEOROLOGICAL APPLICATIONS
LA  - English
KW  - climate risks
KW  - eco-systems
KW  - adaptation
