TI  - Climate risk, policy, and insurance: a forecast-based model for weather index design in vulnerable economies
T2  - INTERNATIONAL ECONOMICS AND ECONOMIC POLICY
LA  - English
KW  - Direct acyclic graphs
KW  - Influence diagram decision model network
KW  - Index insurance forecasting
KW  - Hedging effectiveness
KW  - Bivariate copulas
KW  - AGRICULTURE
