TI  - Impact of climate change on water-related physical events, consequent human migration, and burden of drowning in India: An evidence synthesis
T2  - JOURNAL OF FAMILY MEDICINE AND PRIMARY CARE
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
KW  - drowning
KW  - India
KW  - migration
KW  - sea-level rise
KW  - water-related events
