TI  - Vulnerability analysis of smallholder farmers to climate variability and change: an agro-ecological system-based approach in the Fincha'a sub-basin of the upper Blue Nile Basin of Ethiopia
T2  - ECOLOGICAL PROCESSES
LA  - English
KW  - Vulnerability index
