TI  - Optimizing Nile tilapia stocking density for enhanced water use efficiency and profitability in fish-cabbage integrated farming systems in Northwest Ethiopia
T2  - AQUACULTURE INTERNATIONAL
LA  - English
KW  - Integrated aquaculture-agriculture
KW  - Tilapia
