TI  - ADAPTATION TO CLIMATE CHANGE IN RURAL CHINA TO ENHANCE THE WELFARE EFFECTS OF CLEAN ENERGY TRANSITION CONSIDERING TOPOGRAPHY AND E-COMMERCE
T2  - MANAGEMENT THEORY AND STUDIES FOR RURAL BUSINESS AND INFRASTRUCTURE DEVELOPMENT
LA  - English
KW  - rural clean energy
