TI  - Climate variability and farmer's vulnerability in a flood-prone district of Assam
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF CLIMATE CHANGE STRATEGIES AND MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Vulnerability assessment
KW  - Floods
KW  - Indicators
