TI  - Solar smart grid as a path to economic inclusion and adaptation to climate change in the Brazilian Semiarid Northeast
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF CLIMATE CHANGE STRATEGIES AND MANAGEMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Socioeconomic development
