TI  - A hybrid-epistemological approach to climate change research: Linking scientific and smallholder knowledge systems in the Ecuadorian Andes
T2  - ANTHROPOCENE
LA  - English
KW  - Climate change
KW  - Hybrid epistemology
KW  - Knowledge systems
KW  - Tropical Andes
